been gone all day long,

302
00:16:24,875 --> 00:16:26,250
and she isn't home yet.

303
00:16:26,333 --> 00:16:27,583
Huh?

304
00:16:27,666 --> 00:16:29,083
We've been looking all
over for her, but no luck.

305
00:16:29,166 --> 00:16:30,791
You haven't
seen her have you?

306
00:16:30,875 --> 00:16:33,500
