to find Tomoka.

343
00:18:23,250 --> 00:18:26,375
I should've kept the
pervert around longer, huh?

344
00:18:26,458 --> 00:18:29,250
At least he knows
where my house is.

345
00:18:40,666 --> 00:18:42,083
