350
00:19:04,958 --> 00:19:08,041
I'm alone because
I was mean to people.

351
00:19:17,083 --> 00:19:19,458
Hiding under a bridge.

352
00:19:19,541 --> 00:19:23,250
You've got a lot of
nerve running off like that.

353
00:19:23,333 --> 00:19:26,750
How stupid can you be?

354
00:19:35,583 --> 00:19:39,208
